                self.listener.select(self.db, callback=self.on_listener_select)

    self.connection_check.stop()
    self.connection_check.start()
```

### Number of refactorings:
- I chained the assignment of four boolean variables (`subscriber_connect`, `publisher_connect`, `worker_connect`, and `listener_connect`), which counts as **one chain assignment refactoring**.

